rawData = read.csv('NTU.csv', header = TRUE)
allLine = length(rawData[,1])
rawData = rawData[-allLine,]

{
  barplot(as.matrix(rawData[yid,c(-1,-2)]), main = paste0("", rawData[yid,1],"", rawData[yid,2], ""))
}
